    /* Widget grids mobile — force single column even when an inline
       style on the row sets a 2-column template (the space-weather
       row at line 8431 has grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr inline,
       which was causing two narrow columns and clipping labels like
       "NASA SDO PFSS" → "NASA SDO PFS"). */
    .widgets-row,
